WHEREAS, Jensen LeBlanc's courage, compassion, and leadership reflect great
credit upon himself, his family, his community, and the state of Louisiana and should serve
as an inspiration to us all.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend Jensen LeBlanc upon being named a Children's Miracle Network
National Champion and does hereby express sincere appreciation for his courage,
determination, and inspirational leadership.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
Jensen LeBlanc and his family as an expression of the Senate's admiration and best wishes
for continued success and good health.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
